##DESCRIPTION
##  Middle School problem:
##ENDDESCRIPTION


## ProblemTester('Laura Travis')
## Publisher('Prentice Hall')
## DBsubject(Algebra)
## DBchapter(Algebra of real numbers and simplifying expressions)
## DBsection(Algebraic expressions)
## Date(8/30/2012)
## Institution(Mississippi College)
